snippet.title: Western Battle of Conqueror's Blade
snippet.description:
Sign up for beta in EU and RU territories: https://cb.my.com/promo/lp1/en.html?_...

Conqueror's Blade is a new free-to-play MMO game of medieval warfare - an ambitious hybrid that deploys tactical third-person action within an epic open world of military strategy. Players must vie to become a great warlord and lead their unique civilization to glory. 

Follow us on our social media channels: 
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ConquerorsBlade/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/official_ConqB
Discord: https://discord.gg/98GMF3T 
ВКонтакте: https://vk.com/cb_mailru 
Одноклассники: https://ok.ru/group/54238672912564
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/conquerorsbladeen/

#ConquerorsBlade #CBT
